<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men dāng zài shén miàn qián zuò wán quán rén, yīn yé hé huá shì quán néng de shén.
 cháng cháng shěng chá fán shì qiú wèn, rén shēng lù shàng zhǔ bì zhǐ yǐn.
 wàn zōng sù yuán zhǔ shì gēn, chú tā yǐ wài bié wú zhēn shén.
 tā shì wǒ men shēng mìng de yuán tóu, yòu shì wǒ men yǒng yuǎn de fú fèn.
 fēng zhōng chuán lái jiā yīn, hēi yè lǐ kàn jiàn zǎo chén.
 shén bì xiàng jìng wèi tā de rén shī ēn, wǒ men dāng zuò wán quán rén.</lyrics>
<title>dāng zuò wán quán rén 迦南1068</title>
<hymn_number>1068</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>